data.description: Excellent Renovation Opportunity! Historic Gem compound on famous Frenchmen Street! Could be converted back to double. Original heart pine hardwood floors, stained glass, historic stair cases, and SOARING ceilings. HUGE lot with long side driveway that leads to a large back yard that once had a stable & service building. A half block from the Faubourg Marigny and 5 blocks to French Quarter. X flood zone. Grocery Store, Streetcar line, shops, bars & restaurants a block away.
